  m_text: 'OBJECTIVE:

    Complete tasks, survive gas waves, use antidote voting,
    escape.



    MOBILE CONTROLS:

    Joystick = Move

    INTERACT = Tasks /
    Exit Scan

    TRACE = Agent decisions

    HELP = Instructions

    DEMO = Judge
    tools



    DEMO FLOW:

    1. Complete tasks or use demo tools

    2. Survive
    infection waves

    3. Vote antidote during meetings

    4. Escape before Final
    Hunt



    No hidden role reveal. Infected players become AI agents.'
